#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.startswith.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.str.startswith"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:1
msgid "Test if the start of each string element matches a pattern."
msgstr "测试每个字符串元素的开头是否匹配某个模式。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:3
msgid "Equivalent to :meth:`str.startswith`."
msgstr "等价于 :meth:`str.startswith`。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:5
msgid ""
"Character sequence or tuple of strings. Regular expressions are not "
"accepted."
msgstr "字符序列或字符串元组。不接受正则表达式。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:8
msgid ""
"Object shown if element tested is not a string. The default depends on "
"dtype of the array. For object-dtype, ``numpy.nan`` is used. For the "
"nullable ``StringDtype``, ``pandas.NA`` is used. For the ``\"str\"`` "
"dtype, ``False`` is used."
msgstr ""
"如果测试的元素不是字符串，则显示的对象。默认值取决于数组的 dtype。对于 "
"object-dtype，使用 ``numpy.nan``。对于可空的 ``StringDtype``，使用 ``"
"pandas.NA``。对于 ``\"str\"`` dtype，使用 ``False``。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:14
msgid ""
"A Series of booleans indicating whether the given pattern matches the "
"start of each string element."
msgstr "一个布尔值 Series，指示给定模式是否匹配每个字符串元素的开头。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:20
msgid ":py:obj:`str.startswith`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:21
msgid "Python standard library string method."
msgstr "Python 标准库字符串方法。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:23
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.str.endswith`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:24
msgid "Same as startswith, but tests the end of string."
msgstr "与 startswith 相同，但测试字符串的结尾。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:26
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.str.contains`"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:27
msgid "Tests if string element contains a pattern."
msgstr "测试字符串元素是否包含某个模式。"

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:30
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: of pandas.core.strings.accessor.StringMethods.startswith:55
msgid "Specifying `na` to be `False` instead of `NaN`."
msgstr "指定 `na` 为 `False` 而不是 `NaN`。"

